{"itemid":295,"subject":"A Great Giant Falls","event":"Brad Van Pelt is dead at 57.\r\n\r\nShocking and sad.  He was a great linebacker and a great G-Man whose career, sadly, was squandered on some very bad Giants teams.  But true fans of Big Blue remember him fondly.  We didn't have much to cheer about in those days.","ditemid":75542,"eventtime":"2009-02-21 18:35:00","props":{"personifi_word_count":51,"taglist":"nfl","current_moodid":25,"opt_screening":"F","commentalter":1245440591},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2009-02-22 01:37:54","anum":22,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html","event_timestamp":1235241300,"reply_count":15,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/66560804/11390144","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5509142","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5509142#t5509142","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5509142#t5509142","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5509142#t5509142","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"jimvanpelt","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://jimvanpelt.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5509142,"talkid":21520,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5509142#t5509142","upictitle":"jimvanpelt: Saturn Ring Blues","article":"I scanned my friends' posts quickly, and this one made me do a double take.<br /><br />I have a science fictional connection to Brad Van Pelt.  When I went to my first ever science fiction convention, WorldCon '96, the con volunteer who was signing folks up for kaffeeklatches looked at my name tag and said, \"Are you somebody?\"  I had several small press short story sales at that time, so I thought it was possible he had read something of mine.  But it turned out he was thinking of Brad Van Pelt.<br /><br />I'm sorry he died so young.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 01:49:25 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://jimvanpelt.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"jimvanpelt","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"jimvanpelt","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://jimvanpelt.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"jimvanpelt","ctime_ts":1235267365,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/30340275/5873046","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5510166","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510166#t5510166","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510166#t5510166","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510166#t5510166","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"dadiceguy","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://dadiceguy.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5510166,"talkid":21524,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510166#t5510166","upictitle":"dadiceguy: pic#30340275","article":"Yeah I am from Owosso where he went to high school. Played football with some of his nephews. Had some problems after football, but was always a class act. Damn shame he died so young.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 02:22:38 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://dadiceguy.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"dadiceguy","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"dadiceguy","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://dadiceguy.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"dadiceguy","ctime_ts":1235269358,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/9660739/387266","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5517078","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5517078#t5517078","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5517078#t5517078","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5517078#t5517078","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"darthparadox","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://darthparadox.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5517078,"talkid":21551,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5517078#t5517078","above":5510166,"upictitle":"Darth Paradox: Angel Feather (c) SJGames (INWO)","article":"Apparently a lot of NFL veterans have been dying relatively young (i.e. in their 50s, and occasionally earlier) from \"natural\" causes.  The NFL is actually pretty worried about this - if it turns out that something about a professional football career is taking a decade or so off of players' life expectancies, they've got a huge problem on their hands.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 19:32:53 UTC","parent":5510166,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://darthparadox.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"darthparadox","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"darthparadox","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://darthparadox.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"darthparadox","ctime_ts":1235331173,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/83701858/603128","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5510422","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510422#t5510422","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510422#t5510422","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510422#t5510422","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"jupiter_star","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://jupiter-star.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5510422,"talkid":21525,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5510422#t5510422","upictitle":"Sabrina: Sparkling Rosetta","article":"Yeesh, I barely know a thing about football and I knew who he was. That's so sad to hear!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 02:39:32 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://jupiter-star.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"jupiter_star","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"jupiter_star","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://jupiter-star.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"jupiter_star","ctime_ts":1235270372,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5512726","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5512726#t5512726","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5512726#t5512726","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5512726#t5512726","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"icewind87","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://icewind87.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5512726,"talkid":21534,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5512726#t5512726","upictitle":"icewind87: pic#0","article":"First off, my prayers and condolences to the family of Brad van Pelt. I'm sure he was a great football player.<br /><br />But... I'd also just like to say that ... I also send my best wishes to you Mr. Martin. I have read the past couple threads about the trolls and morons who have been bashing you and the books.<br /><br />I too, have read the comments by the trolls and I'll be honest, it fumed me. You're the best right now in fantasy, and you leave a tough act to follow for everyone else. Your books are master-pieces that can only be appreciated by those who have patience. Not only in waiting for the next book to arrive, but patience in fully understand the depth and beauty of your writing. You are, in my mind atleast, a perfect author who accepts nothing but the best in your writing and what you deliver to your fans.<br /><br />I've posted several comments on youtube, bashing the critics and trolls. One in the Ice Dragon video by Tor/Forge.<br /><br />On a final note... I've read the post page many times about 'Dance' (the one that states the progress and how you don't plan to update it until 'Dance' is done). I have to say, it was sad to hear that you missed conventions in '07 that you haven't missed in over a decade, consistent, in times past. Well... ignore the trolls, ignore the critics, DON'T MISS THE CONVENTIONS. Not only are they fun for you, but they're a unique opportunity for your loyal fans to have a chance to meet their icon. I know I'd love to have an opportunity to meet you. But it is sad to hear that you've broken a long standing record of going to your traditional haunts once a year.<br /><br />At any rate. Didn't mean to detract from the main subject of the thread, if this post is moved I can understand... Keep fighting the good fight, I am eager to read 'Dance' but my better side tells me that the wait is worth it. And when it comes out all will be well, because you are an excellent author who accepts nothing but the best from yourself and the product you give to your fans.<br /><br /><br />A Dedicated Reader,<br />Luke","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 04:43:06 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Prayers and best wishes...","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://icewind87.livejournal.com/","striked":1,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"icewind87","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"icewind87","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://icewind87.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"icewind87","ctime_ts":1235277786,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/20411596/4337561","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5514518","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5514518#t5514518","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5514518#t5514518","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5514518#t5514518","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"fastfwd","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://fastfwd.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5514518,"talkid":21541,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5514518#t5514518","upictitle":"fastfwd: Calgary","article":"The sound you heard was my jaw hitting the floor.<br /><br />No, I'm not generally known as a football fan. But in fact, I've watched a lot of football (American variety). And...well, <i>jeez.</i>","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 10:30:38 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://fastfwd.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"fastfwd","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"fastfwd","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://fastfwd.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"fastfwd","ctime_ts":1235298638,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5515286","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5515286#t5515286","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5515286#t5515286","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5515286#t5515286","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"chuckiefrog","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://chuckiefrog.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livej