17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"proudbronco","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"proudbronco","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://proudbronco.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"proudbronco","ctime_ts":1235333325,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/109915172/10560429","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?replyto=5519126","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5519126#t5519126","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5519126#t5519126","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5519126#t5519126","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"nycfalcon","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://nycfalcon.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":5519126,"talkid":21559,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/75542.html?thread=5519126#t5519126","upictitle":"nycfalcon: pic#109915172","article":"My favorite talk radio show spent most of the afternoon talking about him and taking calls. One was from John Mara who had great things to say about him including about his world class man-about-town personality. Brad took LT under his wing and showed him all the possibilities New York offered. It's too bad that they never had an offense. It's also sad that he had to deal with financial stresses after football. A player with his solid contribution to the NFL should have more than thirty-odd thousand in annual pension to fall back on.<br />","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"8 years ago","ctime":"February 22 2009, 23:18:38 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://nycfalcon.livejournal.com/","striked":nu